sdp/verification/frac-0044-verify.md:17:The implementation follows established patterns: frozen `@dataclass(slots=True)` for `HookRewriteResult` matching other depth-2 result dataclasses in this fractal series, `pathlib.Path` throughout, stdlib-only, no new dependencies. The `HOOK_FIELD_RENAMES` / `HOOK_TARGET_FILES` constants follow the tuple-of-tuples / tuple-of-strings conventions used in the spec. Module docstring and `if __name__ == "__main__"` entry point match the spec contract. `from __future__ import annotations` and `sys.exit(main())` are consistent with other modules in the series.
